values: I never did one of these posts when I first made this journal, so I'm doing one now. My journal is at its core, friends only. I may have a few entries set to public, but if you really want to read my journal, I have to let you in. Comment to be added, lovelies. ♥

I've done another friends cut, trimming out people who I either don't feel I connected with, or haven't posted in a long time.

No hard feelings if I've cut you, and I wish you the best!

Before I make a post about the crazy goddamn day I had, I did a friends list cut. I'm sorry if I deleted you and you feel I shouldn't have - either you hadn't updated in a long time, or we just did not click. 

If you're still here, yay! Glad to have you.
